
Pre-requisites :

1. Hadoop should be up and running.

To Do :

1. Provide exact local path, from where the files to be picked. Local directory path variable is "localFilePath".
2. Provide exact hdfs path, into where the files to be dropped/inserted. Hdfs directory path variable is "hdfsFilePath".
3. Provide exact file name, to be created in hdfs directory. File name variable is "hdfsFileName"

Procedure :

1. Run hadoopUpload.sh to load all you files into hdfs from local file system.